that we collect to deliver advertisements on the Partner Sites. If you wish to opt-out of the use of your Personal Data for displaying Advertisements served through our Advertising Platform please visit our
Opt-Out/Do Not Sell my Information Page
. Opting-out of personalized advertising does not mean you will no longer see online ads, it simply means you will not see ads tailored to your personal interests.
Partner Sites may also provide you regarding the use of cookies and the collection and use of Personal Data. Please consult with their websites for more information.
Non-Discrimination
