Section II. Personal Information Collected
When you access and browse our website, we may collect certain personal information either automatically or voluntarily. We
          categorise collected data as follows:
Cookie Data;
Subscription Data;
Contact Forms Data;
Request a Demo Data;
Case Study Data;
Download a Whitepaper Data;
Reviews Data;
Curated Deals Data;
Data Subject Request Data.
Cookie Data
We collect a variety of data using cookies and various other standard (typical for the industry) technology, including:
Cookies. Cookies are a technology that is based on small-size data files containing a string of alphanumeric characters that
          usually include a unique identifier and are placed on a user’s device or computer. Cookies are usually stored at the user's
          computer permanently (persistent cookies) or temporarily. We use cookies to maintain security , operate the website, show relevant
          advertisements, and optimize user experience.
Tags and Pixels. Tags and Pixels are blocks of code that we may use to track your browsing on the Internet: from resources to any
          particular websites or applications to track your browsing behavior. Sometimes web beacons are used for these purposes as well.
          They are usually transparent or invisible graphic images, no larger than 1x1 pixel, they are placed on a page or otherwise. It is
          often used in combination with cookies.
Cookie Data is categorized as follows:
Essential;
Advertising;
Analytics;
Entertainment;
Functional;
Social.
Essential
We use these cookies to ensure that our website operates correctly (for example, to allow you to adjust your screen size). These
          cookies are essential and cannot be disabled. For more information, please refer to our cookie declaration provided by the CMP
          solution, which is always accessible at the bottom left of the page.
Advertising
We, along with third-party partners, use these cookies or identifiers to collect and track information about your online
          activities. This data allows us to deliver more personalized and relevant advertisements, tailored to your interests and browsing
          behavior. These tracking mechanisms help ensure that the ads you see are more aligned with your preferences, enhancing your
          overall experience. Additionally, third parties may use this information to measure ad performance and to optimize the content and
          services they provide. For more information, please refer to our cookie declaration provided by the
CMP solution
, which is always accessible at the bottom left of the page.
Analytics
We, along with third-party partners, use these cookies or identifiers to analyze how visitors interact with our website. This
          information helps us gain insights into user behavior and website performance, allowing us to enhance and optimize the overall
          user experience, improve functionality, and tailor content to better meet the needs of our visitors. For more information, please
          refer to our cookie declaration provided by the
CMP solution
, which is always accessible at the bottom left of the page.
Entertainment
We, along with third-party partners, use these cookies to deliver and display digital content online and to analyze your
          engagement with that content. This helps us understand how users interact with videos, images, and other media, allowing us to
          optimize content delivery, improve user experience, and provide more relevant and engaging content based on your preferences and
          behavior. For more information, please refer to our cookie declaration provided by the
CMP solution
, which is always accessible at the bottom left of the page.
Functional
We, along with third-party partners, use these cookies to remember your choices and preferences during your visit to our website
          or when you return. These cookies enable us to provide a more personalized experience by retaining settings such as language,
          layout, and other customizations, ensuring a seamless and consistent experience each time you visit. For more information, please
          refer to our cookie declaration provided by the
CMP solution
, which is always accessible at the bottom left of the page.
Social
We, along with third-party social media networks, use these cookies to enable functional integration with your social media
          account and track user profiles across various websites. This allows for seamless sharing of content, interactions with social
          media features directly on our site, and the collection of data about your browsing behavior across different platforms, helping
          to deliver more personalized content and targeted advertising. For more information, please refer to our cookie declaration
          provided by the
CMP solution
, which is always accessible at the bottom left of the page.
Please note that you can adjust your cookie preferences by using the
cookie banner
or visiting the cookie settings page for each relevant domain (e.g. smartyads.com, ssp.smartyads.com). To manage cookies across
          all your browsers and devices, it is necessary to configure the settings individually on each browser and device used to access
          our websites. For more information please see Section Your Choices to Avoid Targeted Advertising below.
