EU-US Data Privacy Framework Participation.
SmartyAds adheres to the EU-U.S. DPF, the UK Extension to the EU-U.S. DPF, and the Swiss-U.S. DPF. As part of this commitment, we
          resolve unresolved complaints regarding our handling of personal data under these frameworks through JAMS, a U.S.-based
          alternative dispute resolution provider.
If we fail to acknowledge your DPF-related complaint promptly or do not resolve it to your satisfaction, you can find more details
          or file a complaint at
https://www.jamsadr.com/DPF-Dispute-Resolution
. JAMS provides these services at no cost to you.
Should your complaint remain unresolved after pursuing these options, you may be eligible to request binding arbitration for
          certain outstanding issues. For further details, please refer to
Annex I of the Data Privacy Framework
.
The Federal Trade Commission (FTC) oversees SmartyAds' compliance with the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework (EU-U.S. DPF) and its UK
          Extension.
SMARTYADS’ LIABILITY IN CASES OF ONWARD TRANSFERS TO THIRD PARTIES
In the context of onward transfers, SmartyAds is responsible for the processing of personal information it receives under the DPF
          Principles and subsequently transfers to a third party acting as its agent. SmartyAds remains liable under the DPF Principles if
          the agent processes such personal information in a way that is inconsistent with these principles unless SmartyAds can demonstrate
          that it is not responsible for the event that caused the damage.
Storage and Sharing of User Information
We do not sell or lease your personal data. Nonetheless, we might disclose your personal data if it's reasonably necessary to
          fulfil our commitments to you and/or for our legitimate interest in maintaining and improving the website. Specifically, your
          personal information may be shared with the following recipient categories:
our affiliates, who may act as data controllers processing your personal data, including their names and contact details, can be
            accessed in the footer;
our subcontractors and team members, such as the support team, or technical team;
third-party solutions that provide us with data storage facilities that are physically located in the United States;
